1037
00:44:18,619 --> 00:44:20,026
Jer "Look Ahead" zvuči optimistično.

1038
00:44:20,028 --> 00:44:22,490
Gledaj pravo. Najebo' si, pogle.

1039
00:44:23,803 --> 00:44:25,818
Um, pre godinu dana,
hteli su da pristanemo

1040
